{"tid":1898871,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"難適應單飛　AKB舊將渡邊麻友傳引退","createTime":"2020-02-26T09:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T06:19:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1e85dc92484583508f6fe334ffcc8276bf796770","tid":1898871,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"日本女團AKB48的25歲前主將渡邊麻友，2017年離隊後，單飛作個人發展，但近月其曝光率大減，加上久未更新社交網，因而傳出引退消息。<br />\n<br />\n曾於2014年AKB人氣總選榮登一姐的渡邊麻友，離隊後轉戰拍劇，去年參演女星廣瀨鈴主演的晨早劇《夏空》後曝光率大減，其個人Fan Club在去年9月突然關閉，官方Twitter自去年除夕後沒有更新。日前，她又以身體不適理由缺席有份主持的TBS台音樂節目《UTAGE!》。有傳她難以適應單飛發展，或會退出藝能界。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200226/bkn-20200226100808501-0226_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200226%2Fbkn-20200226100808501-0226_00862_001.html&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6XzQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=8227bc4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200226/bkn-20200226100808501-0226_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a24c202cc5728695f9267408967977e0e333625f","tid":1898871,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/c3a863af6ce1939724e334b90ec488f0/tumblr_pzgs80MkC61wrnh6go1_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fc3a863af6ce1939724e334b90ec488f0%2Ftumblr_pzgs80MkC61wrnh6go1_1280.jpg&h=81c9adfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9133bbb252dcc249ed03a9aedfad0214e15b5c10","tid":1898871,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"早就應該啦<br />\n果陣成日消費由紀先紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db54f6c4f039b31b3db1a2eef7532876b2d2ea0","tid":1898871,"uid":48783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"麻友is g"},{"pid":"55bb82a6ac544b78b40ff